    The many use cases of the EU Digital Identity Wallet
    • Aangemaakt door Antonios Kamzelas, laatst bijgewerkt door Christos Chartomatsidis op sep 17, 2025 307 minuten leestijd

    Pilot projects

    The many use cases of EU Digital Identity Wallets

    Large Scale Pilots Use Cases

    Discover the many ways that EU Digital Identity Wallets will simplify the lives of citizens and businesses; making data more secure and private. It will also improve security and flexibility for governments and businesses when carrying out transactions online.

    Discover the many ways that EU Digital Identity Wallets will simplify the lives of citizens and businesses; making data more secure and private. It will also improve security and flexibility for governments and businesses when carrying out transactions online.

    Browse use cases

    Mobile Driving Licence

    Request a digital version of your driving licence

    Request a digital version of your driving licence

    Download, store, and share your mobile driving licence; eliminating the need for a physical copy of it.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Accessing government services

    Save time accessing digital public services

    Save time accessing digital public services

    Access digital public services (nationally and across borders) by using your wallet to securely identify and authenticate yourself.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Payments

    Make your online transactions easier

    Make your online transactions easier

    Your wallet offers a single way to identify yourself to all your bank accounts. Easily authorise payments through your wallet.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Nobid
    Visit EWC

    Opening a bank account

    No need to trek down to a bank branch

    No need to trek down to a bank branch

    Verify your identity when opening a new bank account entirely online using just your wallet.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Education certification

    Never lose the diploma you worked so hard for again

    Never lose the diploma you worked so hard for again

    Easily store and share all your education credentials when applying to a new job or university.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit DC4EU

    Health

    Keep your health close at hand

    Keep your health close at hand

    Easily collect prescribed medication at a pharmacy, for yourself or loved ones, even when in another country.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Accessing Social Security benefits

    Verify your social security entitlements

    Verify your social security entitlements

    When working abroad prove that you are covered by your home country's social security. You can also store and share your European Health Insurance Card.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit DC4EU

    SIM Registration

    Registering a new prepaid SIM card just got easier

    Registering a new prepaid SIM card just got easier

    In a new Member State? Use your wallet to easily verify your identity and buy a new prepaid SIM from a local provider.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Travelling

    Store and share key travel documents in your wallet

    Store and share key travel documents in your wallet

    Store your visas, passports and other travel documents in your wallet. Easily check in to flights and hotels.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit EWC

    Signing contracts

    Your wallet makes business flow

    Your wallet makes business flow

    Sign contracts with just your wallet. Create a secure digital signature for any document.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit Potential

    Organisational Digital Identities

    Prove your professional affiliations

    Prove your professional affiliations

    Your wallet lets you prove who you work for when completing transactions in a business context.

    piloted and tested by

    Visit EWC

    What are the Large Scale Pilots?

    Large Scale Pilot projects are currently test driving the many use cases of EU Digital Identity Wallets in the real world.

    Discover the Large Scale Pilots

    Overzicht
    Inhoudshulpmiddelen

    The EU Digital Identity Wallets will provide a safe, reliable, and private means of digital identification for everyone in Europe. Every Member State will provide a wallet to all citizens, residents, and businesses.
